secondary_street_name: And East of 99 Leman Street, Gowers Walk
description: The erection of 212 flats (comprising 33 studio units, 88x1bed, 70x2bed and 21x3bed) in one 5-storey building, two 6-storey buildings and one 7-storey building together with a basement car park providing 112 car parking spaces, 23 motorbike spaces and 104 bicycle spaces.
